---
title: Indian-Spiced Turkey Burgers with Sweet Potato Wedges and Cilantro Yogurt Dip
description: Shake up your at-home burger game! These beautifully spiced turkey burgers get a dose of sweetness from our fig spread. The gentle tartness of the yogurt dip pulls double duty: It adds a layer of flavour to the burger's spring greens and serves as a delicious dip for earthy sweet potatoes.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF211013_R30_W48_CA_RP153360-2_MB_Main_low-720180e2.jpg
